hands_on_practices.solution:
1. 根据定义，空穴的色散关系是
$$E_h(\mathbf{k})=E_0-E_v(\mathbf{k})=E_0-(E_0-\alpha k_x^2-\beta k_y^2-\gamma k_xk_y) = \alpha k_x^2+\beta k_y^2+\gamma k_xk_y.$$
2. 有效质量逆张量是
$$(M_{h,ij}^*)^{-1}=\frac{1}{\hbar^2}\frac{\partial^2E_h}{\partial k_i\partial k_j}
=\frac{1}{\hbar^2}\begin{pmatrix}2\alpha&\gamma\\\gamma&2\beta\end{pmatrix}.$$
3. 令 $A=\begin{pmatrix}2\alpha&\gamma\\\gamma&2\beta\end{pmatrix}$。其特征值 $\lambda_1,\lambda_2$ 满足
$$\det A=(2\alpha)(2\beta)-\gamma^2=4\alpha\beta-\gamma^2,\quad\lambda_1\lambda_2=\det A.$$
因为 $1/m_{h,i}^*=\frac{1}{\hbar^2}\lambda_i$，主有效质量的乘积为
$$m_{h,1}^*m_{h,2}^*=\frac{1}{(1/m_{h,1}^*)(1/m_{h,2}^*)}
=\frac{1}{\bigl(\tfrac{1}{\hbar^2}\lambda_1\bigr)\bigl(\tfrac{1}{\hbar^2}\lambda_2\bigr)}
=\frac{\hbar^4}{\lambda_1\lambda_2}
=\frac{\hbar^4}{4\alpha\beta-\gamma^2}.$$
